or-Everyone-120x53.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Sierra-Buttes-Trail-Stewardship_A-Trail-for-Everyone-768x337.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Sierra-Buttes-Trail-Stewardship_A-Trail-for-Everyone-696x306.jpg 696w\"></a></p><p>The film is a glimpse into their story of working with local small businesses, trail builders, families, and just the people of the communities, bring people together to rejuvenate their livelihoods as they work to bring the planned 300-mile multi-use Lost Sierra Route into reality. <a href=\"https://sierratrails.org/watch-a-trail-for-everyone/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SierraTrails.org</a></p><p><span>More Cycling Advocacy</span></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets.jpg 1280w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-800x500.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-768x480.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-696x435.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-1068x668.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-672x420.jpg 672w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets.jpg 1280w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-800x500.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-768x480.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-696x435.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-1068x668.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/what-are-complete-streets-672x420.jpg 672w\"></a></p><ul><li><strong>US Lawmakers to reintroduce road user Safety &amp; Accessibility Legislation</strong> -Senator Markey and Congressman Cohen are set to reintroduce legislation in the US Congress aiming to improve safety and accessibility for ALL users of the road. Between 2009-2018 pedestrian &amp; bicyclist fatalities increased nearly 51%. In 2019, more than 6000 pedestrians &amp; 800 bicyclists were killed in crashes with motor vehicles. So some of our US representatives are trying to make a difference with their reintroduction of the Complete Streets Act, legislation that would promote safer and more accessible transportation routes across the United States. The legislation would fund &amp; improve more “complete streets” that benefit all users. <a href=\"https://www.markey.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/(2.24.2021)%20Bill%20--%20Complete%20Streets%20Act%202-22-21.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read it all in-depth here</a>, then reach out to your representatives via <a href=\"https://smartgrowthamerica.org/the-complete-streets-act-is-back/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SmartGrowthAmerica.org</a></li></ul><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Endura-Trash-Free-Trails-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><ul><li><strong>Endura supports <em>Trash Free Trails</em>, end to Single Use goods</strong> – Endura pairs up with community-focused <a href=\"https://www.trashfreetrails.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Trash Free Trails</a> non-profit in a bid to both reduce Single Use Product Pollution in &amp; on our trails by 75% over the next four years, and also to simply reconnect people with nature through adventure. Endura will first kit out the TFT team in custom gear, just like their pro athletes, and will support them financially in their clean-up goals. Endura is also working hard on their overall sustainability initiatives, having already planted 1.3 million trees and on track to be CO₂ negative by 2024. Themselves they’re also trying to reduce single-use products with a 15-year-running crash repair service, lots of recycled fabrics across their range, overall garment longevity, 99% packaging recyclability, refillable bio-cleaners &amp; more. Dig in more on Endura’s Sustainability Stories to learn more. <a href=\"https://www.endurasport.com/sustainability/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EnduraSport.com/Sustainability</a></li></ul><p><span>Gear &amp; Gadgets</span></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Restrap-Orange-Fast-straps_orange-is-the-new-black_bikepacking-luggage-strap.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Restrap-Orange-Fast-straps_orange-is-the-new-black_bikepacking-luggage-strap.jpg\" alt=\"Restrap Orange Fast Straps\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1000\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Restrap-Orange-Fast-straps_orange-is-the-new-black_bikepacking-luggage-strap.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Restrap-Orange-Fast-straps_orange-is-the-new-black_bikepacking-luggage-strap.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Restrap-Orange-Fast-straps_orange-is-the-new-black_bikepacking-luggage-strap-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Restrap-Orange-Fast-straps_orange-is-the-new-black_bikepacking-luggage-strap-800x500.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Restrap-Orange-Fast-straps_orang